    {
        "en_raw": "After tomorrow, if we survive? I wish I had your confidence.",
        "en_clean": "After tomorrow, if we survive? I wish I had your confidence.",
        "jp_raw": "王を倒して、まだ生きていたら？ そこまで自信があるとは、うらやましいよ。",
